Entries.default: "By decree of the Queen That Was and the will of the Steel Garrote, you will meet justice."
"I haven't broken any oaths, I swear! You have the wrong man!"
"W-what? But that was over 150 years ago!"
"No, it's not what you think! Duc- Duc Hadret- he forced me! I had no choice!"
"Your bribes fall on deaf ears, oathbreaker. We seek only to exact Woedica's justice."
"Oswald of Aedyr, the court of Woedica has found you guilty."
"You stand accused of the crime of oathbreaking. What say you?"
"Kneel, Oswald, and be tried for your crimes."
"Did you not betray Aedyr, your country of birth, during the War of Defiance?"
"Wait! I can pay you! I can make you all rich! Just- just let me go!"
"May your soul learn from the mistakes of this life as it passes into the next."
